Sheep Tag 2 Content Library — Licensing Overview
================================================

This repository contains two kinds of content, under two different licenses.

1. Community terrains  —  CC BY 4.0
-----------------------------------
The terrain files in the "terrains/" directory (the *.json files and their
embedded preview images) are licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution
4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0). You are free to share and adapt them,
including commercially, as long as you credit the original author (see each
file's "Metadata.Author"). Full terms: terrains/LICENSE and
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

2. Everything else  —  © Luna Wolf Studios LLC, all rights reserved
-------------------------------------------------------------------
All other content in this repository is the proprietary property of
Luna Wolf Studios LLC, Copyright (c) 2017-2026, all rights reserved. This
includes, without limitation:
  - the website source code and configuration;
  - all Sheep Tag 2 artwork, logos, icons, backgrounds, farm art, screenshots,
    and other images (e.g. logos/, icons/, farms/, socials/, history/);
  - the site text and legal documents.
This material may not be copied, modified, redistributed, or used to create
derivative works without the prior written permission of Luna Wolf Studios LLC.

Contributions
-------------
By submitting a terrain to this repository, you confirm it is your original
work and agree to license it under CC BY 4.0.

